  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "キャプテン翼VSは、グラフィックリサーチが開発し、テクモが出版したスポーツゲームで、1992年に日本でリリースされました。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "Captain Tsubasa VS is a soccer RPG/Strategy hybrid that plays out in a cinematic perspective. The game is based on the popular Japanese manga/anime of the same name and was released exclusively to Japan. As the game's title states, the game has a versus mode, which allows two Game Boys to be linked for 2-player versus play.\n\nCaptain Tsubasa VS is a prequel to the first Famicom game and plays identical to other Captain Tsubasa games published by Tecmo.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
